data.description: Home is being sold As Is, Where Is. Please submit offers. Mid-Century Modern home remodeled downstairs in 2019, 2023 new carpet upstairs.  Seller is motivated,  Floor to ceiling windows, replaced plumbing, electrical, ductwork and HVAC, tankless water heater, per seller. Engineered hardwood floors throughout the downstairs, primary en-suite bathroom with two custom cabinets and Quartz countertops, walk-in show and a huge walk-in closet. Large family room with a wall of 10' windows look out at the pool size backyard. Chef's kitchen has an island cooktop, breakfast bar, a spacious breakfast room, beautiful cabinetry, lots of windows and sliding glass doors open to covered patio and second yard. Study can be a fourth bedroom has built-in cabinets. Upstairs has a landing that can be a kids space or another study. Two bedrooms up share a Hollywood bathroom between them which offers two separate sinks and toilets. Zoned to exemplary Frostwood Elementary, Memorial Middle and High schools.
